      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a super reliable ride that's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure, you've found it! This car is in really solid shape and runs like a total dream. It\u2019s been my trusty companion for a while now, and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. Perfect for zipping around town or hitting the open road. Come take it for a test drive\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a linear power delivery that peaks at a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, ensuring long-term structural and mechanical integrity. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for maximum traction under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-intended poise with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the communicative steering and balanced weight distribution the E46 is renowned for. While displaying a light patina from dedicated road use, the vehicle remains in excellent mechanical health and is primed for spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Minor interior wear. Reliable engine.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though a keen eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the navigation system\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent professional inspection confirming the engine runs smooth and the transmission shifts crisply. We recently replaced the brake pads and performed a full synthetic oil change. It is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garaged throughout its ownership. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality ride that has been treated with genuine respect, this vehicle is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This model has been curated for the discerning driver who values mechanical integrity alongside a sophisticated aesthetic. Meticulously maintained and prepared for immediate delivery, it offers a superior driving experience at a competitive market valuation.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my favorite ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and is ready to hit the road today. It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and dependability. I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a masterclass in mid-engine balance. Powered by a 3.4L flat-six, this 987.1 generation features a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and an exceptionally communicative hydraulic steering rack. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a factory-spec suspension that manages weight transfer with surgical precision. Maintenance is current, including a recent cooling system overhaul and fresh rotors for the four-piston monobloc calipers. While showing minor patina consistent with enthusiastic use, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering linear power delivery and a visceral exhaust note. A pure driver\u2019s tool ready for the canyon or the track.",
